                                        Specifications

                                    TRAINING CARD 1 CRUD with SQL

Managing a database with one table :

        Customer, with fields ID, first name, last name Perform CRUD operations on the data

        Show the content of the table with an URL

        No need to manage security (login, ...)


Techniques :

        H2 database management system

        Eclipse project with Maven for building the app and managing dependencies JDBC / SQL to access the data


Aim :

        Build a project with maven
        Design a basic database management project with separated layers Use a simple RDBMS


Duration :

        1 week


Questions :

        What are the basic maven commands to build and deploy a project ? What is the interest of using H2 ?
